Pre-Game Insights: Bosnia-Herzegovina and Hungary are competing in the 2024-25 UEFA Nations League League A.
Bosnia are looking to avoid relegation, while Hungary aim to improve their standings.
Key players include Dominik Szoboszlai for Hungary and Edin Dzeko for Bosnia.
The match is crucial for both teams' tournament progression.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This is the first meeting between the teams in the Nations League since 2008.
Bosnia have a poor head-to-head record against Hungary.
